Package: libcmaesr
Title: R Interface to 'libcmaes'
Version: 0.1
Authors@R: c(
    person("Marc", "Becker", , "marcbecker@posteo.de", role = c("cre", "aut"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-8115-0400"))
  )
Copyright: See the file COPYRIGHTS for Eigen and libcmaes copyright details
Description: A lightweight R interface to the 'libcmaes' C++ library for Covariance Matrix Adaptation Evolution Strategy (CMA-ES). It allows for the optimization of black-box functions using the CMA-ES algorithm and its variants. Includes vendored copies of Eigen (MPL-2.0) and libcmaes (LGPL-3+); see inst/COPYRIGHTS.
License: LGPL-3
URL: https://github.com/berndbischl/libcmaesr
BugReports: https://github.com/berndbischl/libcmaesr/issues
