    R (>= 3.1.0)
Imports:
    checkmate (>= 2.0.0),
    mlr3misc (>= 0.15.1)
Suggests:
    testthat (>= 3.0.0)
SystemRequirements: C++17
Config/testthat/edition: 3
Config/testthat/parallel: false
Encoding: UTF-8
Language: en-US
